title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: All eyes are on Nike (NKE) due to release earnings this week, after overcoming grim expectations in the previous quarter. Semiconductor company Micron Technology (MU) will report third quarter results, after seeing shares fall sharply since the start of June. The most influential blockchain & crypto event in Europe is taking place after a COVID hiatus.
